text: The Cuervos de Ensenada JAP Fútbol Club, commonly known as Cuervos de Ensenada, is a Mexican football club based in Ensenada, Baja California. The club was founded on 2016, and recently plays in the Liga Premier de Ascenso of Segunda División de México. == Players == === Current squad === == References == == External links == * Category:Ensenada, Baja California Category:Association football clubs established in 2016 Category:Football clubs in Baja California Category:2016 establishments in Mexico Category:Segunda División de México
